{% assign made_better_desc = "
<b>organic.</b> Free from pesticides, dyes, chemical fertilizers (ew) & other synthetic additives. Guaranteed.
<b>all-natural.</b> No synthetic additives, only ingredients from nature. We like it natural :)
<b>gluten-free.</b> This one's easy ;) Products marked gluten-free do not contain gluten.
<b>cruelty-free.</b> We do not & will not participate in harming animals. All of our makesy products are cruelty-free, always.
<b>allergen-free.</b> Sayin' no to common allergens with products free of wheat, gluten, fish or shellfish, egg, soy, peanut or tree nut ingredients or traces.
<b>sustainably-made.</b> Manufactured using renewable ingredients & practices, like our wooden wicks, which come from FSC Certified mills!
<b>biodegradable.</b> Can be decomposed naturally by bacteria or other living organisms! How cool?!
<b>recyclable.</b> Simple. 100% recyclable & eager to be converted into new things ;) In fact, all of our packaging materials are recyclable (at minimum)!
<b>vegan.</b> Vegan products contain no animal products or animal-derived ingredients. Nada. None. Zero.
<b>diacetyl-free.</b> Associated with damaging lung function, diacetyl is a flavoring agent. Flavors sold by makesy absolutely, 100% do not contain diacetyl.
<b>toxin-free.</b> Various categories of toxins can pose adverse health effects from exposure. We're proud to say that our products do not contain reproductive, acute or organ toxins. No way!
<b>phthalate-free.</b> Phthalates are lil scent carriers that help scents linger longer. Some types of phthalates have affected the reproductive system of laboratory animals. We ain't about that, so none of our fragrances contain phthalates.
<b>mutagen-free.</b> Chemicals or physical agents that can change our genetic makeup in a harmful way? Nope. Not about it. Exposure to mutagens can produce DNA mutations that contribute to disease, that's why none of our products contain them.
<b>carcinogen-free.</b> Ingredients on the California Prop 65 list are are known to cause cancer, birth defects or other reproductive harm - no thanks. None of our fragrances require Prop 65 labeling.
<b>paraben-free.</b> Parabens are a family of related (icky) chemicals that are commonly used as preservatives in cosmetic products. See ya never! Our makesy products are always specially formulated without parabens.  
